To add theses files in your mod, drag n' drop in your <bo3 root>/share/raw folder, or mods/your_mods folder,
in your .zone, add :
  rawfile,<file path>/<file>.lua
  
in your hud.lua :
  require("<file path with '.' replacing '/'>.<file>")


Done :
